title: Humans& thinks coordination is the next frontier for AI, and they’re building a model to prove it
description: Humans&, a new startup founded by alumni of Anthropic, Meta, OpenAI, xAI, and Google DeepMind, is building the next generation of foundation models for collaboration, not chat.
